# Whitelist-Modell: standardmaessig alles ignorieren
*

# Repo-Metadaten und Kernfiles erlauben
!.gitignore
!.github/
!.github/**
!README.md
!CLAUDE.md
!CHANGELOG.md
!docker-compose.yml
!index.md

# Arbeitsbereiche erlauben
!docs/
!docs/**
!scripts/
!scripts/**
!agent/
!agent/**
!growbox/
!growbox/**
!systemd/
!systemd/**
!infra/
!infra/openclaw.json

# Explizite Blacklist fuer bekannte sensible/volatile Inhalte
.env
.env.bak
secrets.env
*.key
*.pem
pihole/config/
homeassistant/config/
esphome/config/
esphome/config/secrets.yaml
mosquitto/config/passwd
mosquitto/data/
mosquitto/log/
tailscale/state/
infra/openclaw-data/
infra/portainer_data/
agent/skills/skill-manager/.state/
agent/memory/
backups/
caddy/data/
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.log
homeassistant/config/home-assistant_v2.db
homeassistant/config/home-assistant.log*
docs/operations/doc-keeper-latest.md

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
